      "title": "My cartoon for this week&rsquo;s New Scientist magazine",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s640x960/4c2c18a0bcca742ac9ee4bd2b314f535bb479220.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"870\" data-orig-width=\"1299\" alt=\"Two scientists walk through a cluttered old-fashioned science laboratory.  The female scientist says  &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;Analogue instruments! Paper records! Chalk boards! I thought you'd agreed to modernise the laboratory?&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D;  The male scientist replies &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;That's what i'm so excited about: we have moved to cloud-based storage for our data!&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D;  They step out onto a balcony. She says: &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;Please tell me you haven't built a library zeppelin&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D;   This is exactly what he has done. It floats across the sky and he adds &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;It's got a fax machine!&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s75x75_c1/7e3239b57fe9430c48aae9a7854c5c43163ffa63.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s100x200/604b9f9862ed15ddde02c72568a76a19f05e82f1.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s250x400/731617947f952f4c3732ce065bf8c657d0b94ca8.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s400x600/099a4ec4ca1fc9254f56ddd171dd44cff1223656.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s500x750/b1473c9ca3c6b85b7ecbe593b07471865e7e0d75.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s540x810/2325f232aaff6ba95f8e1435765502934c7851b5.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s640x960/4c2c18a0bcca742ac9ee4bd2b314f535bb479220.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/274bc4573ce1daf60b98b54750c82e1b/279d93c4b098acdc-86/s1280x1920/cc730b60f566cf4bd535ecb6b35fe46