    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/809884456385216512",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/809884456385216512",
      "title": "My cartoon for this week&rsquo;s @guardian books",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s640x960/028d7b469217580b3df25f6340467d779ec3f48f.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"830\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Three panels showing a bench on a small hill in London on a grey drizzly day. A man in a fedora carrying a suitcase arrives, then he is joined by a woman carrying an umbrella and a man in dark glasses reading a newspaper. They all look shifty and hurriedly converse: &quot;Good.&quot; &quot;Very.&quot; &quot;Agreed.&quot; Then they all walk off down the hill.  Caption: Every month, the Espionage Book Club discuss a classic work of spy fiction at a clandestine meeting. To minimise the risk of exposure, infiltration or surveillance by hostile agents, conversation is restricted to the essentials.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s75x75_c1/e3c338fca1c69bfe474195924a50be83875611c1.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s100x200/143a075e9b61cad319f2f35d1951270afb1421b0.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s250x400/ec59fd1419ef15e56e083e8713814e759248bacd.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s400x600/cba1eea2b6cb21ec13c89949cc5a73edb6d753da.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s500x750/2d37d7394ac02b5237ae0914d4c47420c8886770.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s540x810/83ca720ee2abf526f4c52d89ee75abc52dfb5d33.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s640x960/028d7b469217580b3df25f6340467d779ec3f48f.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776678514e371a164f6ef66c2f101b5b/ca1f18ded11688d6-1f/s1280x1920/f0f8f810a2ee04f98a0b1d016b35ff739a1ae68b.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/776