    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/809802410044391424",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/809802410044391424",
      "title": "My cartoon for this week&rsquo;s New Scientist ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s640x960/f639c2e2fe41f4790c256bab56dea0e3ba78ced3.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"827\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"Two scientists look at a monitor attached to a large apparatus consisting of pipes, tanks, vessels and hoses.   The first scientist says &quot;I don't get it. The reaction is running perfectly, but we can't account for 7% of the heat.&quot;  The other says &quot;Have you Asked the Professor?&quot;  The first replies &quot;We're not supposed To disturb him when He's in his office.&quot;   On the other side of the apparatus, one of the pipes goes through a wall into another room where it warms the water for a hot tub in which the professor relaxes.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s75x75_c1/c8c32fdccd58a2d8993cfbc0e42e75fe1c5601e0.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s100x200/2565d9017653a0367b7731d9af35b6568bbcf5c7.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s250x400/eec2e5f0cca883a3e7cd4009d1ec2d21aa7a7e2d.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s400x600/429f1064027c3f61613f599f6e134dd04aad1a36.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s500x750/b734bfd5d98054a44b13b5a4d270c0b8b7e7eb3e.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s540x810/888935bb7a9481b06c6105e983ed322372f7d97a.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s640x960/f639c2e2fe41f4790c256bab56dea0e3ba78ced3.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/c172c4f85e0ea398d8c7dd4ae07877fd/edd9d357a27e993f-d6/s1280x1920/44b93411e9ad556b12bb70286bf5e8bb9aa3e192.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
